        "subject": "LU-4271 mdd: do not start journal handle before quota ops",
        "message": "LU-4271 mdd: do not start journal handle before quota ops\n\nBefore this patch, dead-lock situations have been encountered in\nJBD2 layer, due to mdd_attr_set() routine calling heavy quota\nprocessing routines, inside a journal handle reservation.\nThis bug only concerns mdd_attr_set() routine, and only in\nb2_1 version.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I2c9e2c54f0525f662398baef41445f66a271cbed\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
